, roughhousing and"],[2790,2911,"stirring up drama,"],[2932,3169,"and you're so chill."],[3199,3424,"And such a gentleman."],[3557,3728,"How do you hang out with"],[3728,3870,"someone like Rowan?"],[3974,4170,"Well, we grew up together,"],[4170,4312,"so I guess I had a"],[4354,4529,"lot of time to get used to Rowan."],[4696,4742,"Hm."],[4796,4938,"So I guess he was always"],[4954,5117,"picking on you and stuff, right?"],[5213,5251,"No."],[5292,5347,"Actually,"],[5347,5459,"he was always the one to, like,"],[5497,5659,"step up and protect us."]],"59":[[100,208,"I know he seems bossy,"],[237,333,"but I, I think it's just"],[333,504,"because he's really loyal."],[654,713,"I mean,"],[771,834,"you know, once he becomes"],[834,913,"your friend and"],[1013,1121,"he'll give you everything he's got."],[1251,1397,"You know, I see that, actually."],[1468,1601,"It's like the things he says"],[1601,1726,"are so nasty,"],[1726,1997,"and then his actions are different."],[2068,2318,"He's kind of a big softie, huh?"],[2531,2606,"Seems like you and Rowan"],[2606,2736,"got a lot closer while I was gone."],[3019,3203,"Yeah, some things happened"],[3240,3374,"that made me see him differently."],[3578,3807,"He's actually not so terrible."],[4179,4245,"Em."],[4287,4354,"Mhm."],[4504,4621,"Are you in love with Rowan?"]],"60":[[41,95,"Uh..."],[479,571,"Uh..."],[646,992,"I don't belong in his world."],[1080,1159,"That's not an answer."],[1197,1372,"Well, he's so"],[1434,1626,"rude and mean."],[1710,1926,"So, why would I have feelings"],[1926,2027,"for someone like that?"],[2043,2202,"Emma, that's not an answer, either."],[2723,2773,"You okay?"],[2802,2886,"Yeah, it's just a cold."],[2915,3069,"You sure? You don't look so good."],[3399,3503,"Thank you, Doctor Parker."],[4212,4266,"You know,"],[4291,4475,"Emma, I think you are the most"],[4475,4637,"amazing person."],[4750,4954,"You're brave, you're kind."],[5042,5117,"You stand out for people,"],[5117,5217,"even when it's hard."],[5242,5326,